cast.overview: A man without attachments or responsibilities suddenly finds himself with an abandoned baby and leaves for London to try and find the mother. Eight years later after he and his daughter become inseparable Gloria's mother reappears.
cast.title: Two Is a Family

details.biography:
Alice David (born 22 March 1987) is a French actress, known for the television series Bref (2011) and the film Babysitting (2014). She is the voice of the French dub of Lara Croft in the video game Tomb Raider
